s/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba8a364b4143d72c4ad5380936c47ed6453ca21","tid":6681,"uid":19714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:13:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Powerbeats 3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBeats d聲唔會好垃圾咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTopic 係藍芽耳機....首先音質都唔好要求咁高啦，X3網上普遍都話好聲過Powerbeat3 ，但又未好到要即刻射出黎個隻。再講你用既係iPhone , 粒W1俾到你既慳電同連接性我又覺得powerbeats係值得買過X3。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 訂左powerbeats3今日到，今晚再話俾你聽d聲點。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見佢話用到12個鐘同差電快都心郁想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n覺得點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啦，岩岩到手，用左幾個鐘就簡評下。<br />\n<br />\n1) 連接性: 好好，幾個apple devices 真係可以seamlessly 不停轉換<br />\n2) 電量: 尚可，用個幾鐘無左10% <br />\n3) 通話: 好好，我戴住口罩係車來車往既十字路口講電話都非常清晰，我要強調真係好清<br />\n4) 舒適度: 麻麻，可能因為新機，耳勾舊膠有d硬。有d難戴，但比想像中輕身同細<br />\n5) 隔音: 麻麻，可能因為我之前用開Shure 有關<br />\n6) 音量: 麻麻，Shure 我平時開一半音量，呢個要開8成，可能因為Shure隔音實在太出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7) 音色: 尚可接受, 典型Beats音色啦，人聲靠後，bass 都有d力既，係實在既。但實在還實在，做運動我會略嫌bass力水依然唔夠，所以我都略為失望。總括黎講，佢唔係差，但你都唔好期望太高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟初心者一名，只有一部謹有既Shure 215做比較，我知有線唔可以同無線比，但有錯勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總括黎講，你買呢部機既理由只有粒W1帶俾你既電量同連接性，通話方便都幾驚喜既 , 至於其他就唔好期望咁高啦。<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/161252_d0bbb56e3779fbc6050f83acce231314.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F161252_d0bbb56e3779fbc6050f83acce231314.jpg&h=8c143bc4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c38c3e129c04b033a701b06cabe75da76d10a9fa","tid":6681,"uid":19714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T08:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Powerbeats 3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nBeats d聲唔會好垃圾咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTopic 係藍芽耳機....首先音質都唔好要求咁高啦，X3網上普遍都話好聲過Powerbeat3 ，但又未好到要即刻射出黎個隻。再講你用既係iPhone , 粒W1俾到你既慳電同連接性我又覺得powerbeats係值得買過X3。<br />\n<br />\n利申: 訂左powerbeats3今日到，今晚再話俾你聽d聲點。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n見佢話用到12個鐘同差電快都心郁想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用緊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n覺得點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好啦，岩岩到手，用左幾個鐘就簡評下。<br />\n<br />\n1) 連接性: 好好，幾個apple devices 真係可以seamlessly 不停轉換<br />\n2) 電量: 尚可，用個幾鐘無左10% <br />\n3) 通話: 好好，我戴住口罩係車來車往既十字路口講電話都非常清晰，我要強調真係好清<br />\n4) 舒適度: 麻麻，可能因為新機，耳勾舊膠有d硬。有d難戴，但比想像中輕身同細<br />\n5) 隔音: 麻麻，可能因為我之前用開Shure 有關<br />\n6) 音量: 麻麻，Shure 我平時開一半音量，呢個要開8成，可能因為Shure隔音實在太出色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n7) 音色: 尚可接受, 典型Beats音色啦，人聲靠後，bass 都有d力既，係實在既。但實在還實在，做運動我會略嫌bass力水依然唔夠，所以我都略為失望。總括黎講，佢唔係差，但你都唔好期望太高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟初心者一名，只有一部謹有既Shure 215做比較，我知有線唔可以同無線比，但有錯勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總括黎講，你買呢部機既理由只有粒W1帶俾你既電量同連接性，通話方便都幾驚喜既 , 至於其他就唔好期望咁高啦。<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/161252_d0bbb56e3779fbc6050f83acce231314.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F161252_d0bbb56e3779fbc6050f83acce231314.jpg&h=fe3a1da3&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能未煲夠，煲多一兩日可能會好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffa998b3d27ea17808f279403803f991db70fd8","tid":6681,"uid":4509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:00:25.000Z","msg":"藍芽來講正就B&amp;O H5"},{"pid":"5aab8ca4a9bf3542342b067d1e65de479e8079c5","tid":6681,"uid":4509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藍芽來講正就B&amp;amp;O H5</blockquote><br />\nBose soundsport wireless都ok"},{"pid":"57f87373aa9b880b31f2e4591149a15d6d58366d","tid":6681,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:15:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>jaybird x3 同 freedom 邊隻好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同問，假設價錢一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網上面無咩網評測過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ae411a4e6a8dccc4c344943e6bfedc46ae9fba","tid":6681,"uid":5232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bvlxdnam\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbvlxdnam&h=e2f257ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rylzhjax\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frylzhjax&h=c4dc404e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買果時800蚊 聲就唔算好好，不過有得聽8粒鐘算係咁"},{"pid":"065d08f829110d3a600b8cade205d75e786a6ecf","tid":6681,"uid":17071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T11:24:09.000Z","msg":"bose qc35， 自閉無敵"},{"pid":"19f9755e162484c3a1c6bdb863c0d9d94e5d6c31","tid":6681,"uid":5070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T13:20:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab327a5c2565d223f42dc7002d7ea14438546678","tid":6681,"uid":21623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,